qMeta.description:
The memory footprint of an app when reloaded. 
Note that in practice, this is the baseline memory consumed by an app. As users make selections and navigate the app, additional memory will be cached by the app.

qMeta.title: App Contains Synthetic Keys
qMeta.description:
Indicates if an app's data model contains one or more synthetic keys.
A synthetic key is created when two or more fields are found in two or more tables within an app data model.

qMeta.title: App Contains Data Island(s)
qMeta.description:
Indicates if an app contains one or more island tables in the data model.
An island table is one which does not share any common field with another table and, therefore, is not associated with other data tables.

qMeta.description: 'The ID of the reload task.'

variables.qDefinition:
=If(
	$(vUsingEndpoints),
    'Count({<DataConnectionType-={' & chr(39) & 'qix-datafiles.exe' & chr(39) & '}>}DISTINCT AppID)',
    'Count({<DataConnectionType-={' & chr(39) & 'qix-datafiles.exe' & chr(39) & '},DataConnectionName-={' & chr(39) & '[Unknown Endpoints Connection]' & chr(39) & '}>}DISTINCT AppID)'
)

'The data from the ''Console Settings Collector'' is not currently loaded into this app, which provides the feature/capability settings for each tenant.'& Chr(10) & Chr(10) & 'To load this data, you can toggle on the ''vConsoleSettingsCollector'' variable within the ''**Optional Configuration**'' tab of the load script.'
ValueList('Alerts','API Keys','Automations','Chart Sharing via Email','Dynamic Views','Groups','ML Endpoints','Notes','ODAG','Offline','Report Subscription','Usage Metrics')

If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Alerts',Count({<AlertsEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='API Keys',Count({<APIKeysEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Automations',Count({<AutomationsEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Chart Sharing via Email',Count({<SharingEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Dynamic Views',Count({<DynamicViewEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Groups',Count({<GroupCreationEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Lineage',Count({<LineageEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='ML Endpoints',Count({<MLEndpointsEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Notes',Count({<NotesEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='ODAG',Count({<ODAGEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Offline',Count({<OfflineEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Report Subscription',Count({<SharingReportSubscriptionEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID),
If($(vFeaturesValueList)='Usage Metrics',Count({<UsageMetricsEnabled={'True'}>} TenantID)
)))))))))))))
